{"tid":1879571,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"北市公布居家檢疫失聯3遊客名單 8日香港入境","createTime":"2020-02-14T09:22:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-14T10:12:41.000Z","uid":110351,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"637e4b26b8e3a83f79bfe13fcb267aa1815f0113","tid":1879571,"uid":110351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T09:22:43.000Z","msg":"台北市副市長黃珊珊14日說，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>從香港入境台灣的3名遊客需居家檢疫，3人自8日入境後即失聯，居家檢疫聯絡地點、電話也是假資料</strong></span></span>，詢問中央後決定公布姓名等資訊，盼民眾協尋。（圖取自台北市民政局網頁ca.gov.taipei）<br />\n<br />\n（中央社記者劉建邦台北14日電）台北市副市長黃珊珊今天說，從香港入境台灣的3名遊客需居家檢疫，3人自8日入境後失聯至今，居家檢疫聯絡地點、電話也是假資料，詢問中央後決定公布姓名等資訊，盼民眾協尋。<br />\n<br />\n武漢肺炎疫情嚴峻，黃珊珊下午在北市災害應變中心主持「因應2019新型冠狀病毒疫情小組第8次應變會議」，模擬北市發生社區感染案時開設流行疫情指揮中心情境。黃珊珊會後受訪時，做以上表示。<br />\n<br />\n黃珊珊指出，3名遊客8日從香港入境台灣後，需居家檢疫14天，經防疫人員聯繫2次以上，並透過警政機關協尋，都未找到人，事後發現3人的填寫居家檢疫聯絡地址、電話是不實資料，像地址為萬華區武昌街、電話是中華電信客服，認為3人刻意填寫假資料。<br />\n<br />\n黃珊珊表示，經詢問中央後，決定公布3人姓名、性別等資訊，希望民眾協尋，3人姓名為陳寶珠、張君諾、張龍華，性別為女、男、男，國籍未知，入境時間為2月8日，由香港入境台灣。<br />\n<br />\n黃珊珊說，因中央規定不可公布3人年齡、國籍，擔憂僅公布姓名等資料，會造成民眾協尋困難，並呼籲若有發現3名失聯者，可打1922或台北市防疫專線02-2375-3782。民政局也在官網公布3名失聯者相關資料。<br />\n<br />\n世界衛生組織（WHO）2月11日把武漢肺炎定名為COVID-19（2019年冠狀病毒疾病）。（編輯：李亨山）1090214<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/202002145007.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cna.com.tw%2Fnews%2Ffirstnews%2F202002145007.aspx&d=NEgIrN0XKBZxjsPVzjJKR29Dn5prBKp8mj11ELPip4s%3D&h=61a8c73f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/202002145007.aspx</a>"},{"pid":"08265bd24522bb735eb845bbcbd1799871830edf","tid":1879571,"uid":110351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T09:23:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://imgcdn.cna.com.tw/www/WebPhotos/1024/20200214/880x277_48281355899.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgcdn.cna.com.tw%2Fwww%2FWebPhotos%2F1024%2F20200214%2F880x277_48281355899.jpg&h=09e9cdf0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7df33d3213708edb5bfdbda08c848bceddbcdfa1","tid":1879571,"uid":173598,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T09:24:16.000Z","msg":"支國人<br />\n唔洗check IP"},{"pid":"6c34c956904ef464722cd9745422eafe61a6008d","tid":1879571,"uid":49018,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T09:24:43.000Z","msg":"國籍未知<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98756e69269762780ace97ad8f68d0aef7001488","tid":1879571,"uid":124212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T09:25:47.000Z","msg":"影衰香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e7d58961bf0a4493691a5b3b4a7aab17c0a70c2","tid":1879571,"uid":117422,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T09:26:15.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">地址為萬華區武昌街、電話是中華電信客服</span><br />\n成家都係賤種 <br />\n希望台灣永遠唔俾佢哋再入境"},{"pid":"8aac2e97c7f2b56aaf68044f6928f8d994b38af5","tid":1879571,"uid":10703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T09:38:26.000Z","msg":"扣留呢3個人，叫港共拎陳同佳黎交換<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a202b1cd5d367113703358e8dff680ccb6a07ed1","tid":1879571,"uid":3080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T09:39:47.000Z","msg":"試下打俾天經問問<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf9dfbc1d96ad3bb066263efe18f8dfaa16d0805","tid":1879571,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T09:40:52.000Z","msg":"西門町好危險<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30ddb79fcf56eacea272f7b2f52af218418d0b6b","tid":1879571,"uid":329698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"98756e69269762780ace97ad8f68d0aef7001488","tid":1879571,"uid":124212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T09:25:47.000Z","msg":"影衰香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"repl